1 of the most impactful 🎥🎬 videos I ever filmed in 2023, 
  Seeing my family/loved ones pass away is always hard.  I couldn’t make my auntie funeral, so I came down to Greenville Ms 2days early to film my auntie wake & get footage/memories. 
 Not only that, but get a chance to see my lil cousin Lil Bert who also got a chance to see his Grandma for the last time. Catching those moments meant so much to me & my family. R.I.P Bernadine Hinton Emphry, & Niaomi Hinton Thompson, also Ms Clara Hinton  Roy Lee Hinton & Willie Lee Hinton we must never forget. 🙏🏾✨
